{"lemma":"بَصَرُ","slug":"بَصَرُ","root":"ب.ص.ر","root_slug":"ب-ص-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ص-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"بَصَر","root":"بصر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":48},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n2635","n2636","n2642","n2643","n2644","n2645"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to see"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to see"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make (someone) see","tags":["ditransitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of بَصِرَ (baṣira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vision, sight, gaze","examples":[{"text":"إِذْ جَاؤُوكُمْ مِنْ فَوْقِكُمْ وَمِنْ أَسْفَلَ مِنْكُمْ وَإِذْ زَاغَتْ الأَبْصَارُ وَبَلَغَتْ الْقُلُوبُ الْحَنَاجِرَ وَتَظُنُّونَ بِاللّٰهِ الظُّنُونَا","english":"[Remember] when they came at you from above you and from below you, and when the gazes shifted, and the hearts reached the throats and you assumed about Allah assumptions."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n2635","headword_ar":"بَصُرَ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (Sb, M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSira","text_ar":"بَصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":",] (Lh, K, ) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biSaArapN","text_ar":"بِصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He saw;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became seeing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaAra muboSirFA","text_ar":"صَارَ مُبْصِرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Sb, M, K;) with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"prefixed to the noun following. (K.) But see 4, in four places."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSura","text_ar":"بَصُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is seldom used to signify the sense of sight unless to this meaning is conjoined that of mental perception. (B.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSura","text_ar":"بَصُرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSira","text_ar":"بَصِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, endowed with mental perception;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"belief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firm belief;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge, understanding, intelligence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skill."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurabihi","text_ar":"بَصُرَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S Msb, B,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSirabihi","text_ar":"بَصِرَبِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurahu","text_ar":"بَصُرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSirahu","text_ar":"بَصِرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but more chastely with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bi","text_ar":"بِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSaArapN","text_ar":"بَصَارَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSarN","text_ar":"بَصَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb;) and *"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbSrhu","text_ar":"ابصرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He perceived it mentally;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(B;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he knew it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"understood it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSurotu bimaA lamo yaboSuruwA bihi","text_ar":"بَصُرْتُ بِمَا لَمْ يَبْصُرُوا بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xx. 96], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I knew that which they knew not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSara AlA^adiymayoni","text_ar":"بَصَرَ الاَدِيمَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSorN","text_ar":"بَصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put the two hides together, and sewed them, like as the two edges of a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, are sewed, one being put upon the other; which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mode of sewing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is contrary to,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"different from, that in which a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, is sewed before it is sewed the second time:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put together the two edges of the two hides, when they were being sewed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like as a garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth, is sewed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["Sb","M","K","Lh","T","S"]},{"entry_id":"n2636","headword_ar":"بصّر","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a whelp)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opened his eyes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bS~rhu","text_ar":"بصّرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboSiyrN","text_ar":"تَبْصِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or *"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbSrhu","text_ar":"ابصرهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (accord. to some copies of the K; [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muboSirN","text_ar":"مُبْصِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as confirmatory of the latter; but both seem to be correct;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made him"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to see,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have sight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to have mental perception,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skill:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaEalahu baSiyrFA","text_ar":"جَعَلَهُ بَصِيرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b2-  And the former, (K,) inf. n. as above, (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to know."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baS~arotuhu bihi","text_ar":"بَصَّرْتُهُ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb,) inf. n. as above, (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made him to know it; acquainted him with it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bS~rhu AlA^amora","text_ar":"بصّرهُ الاَمْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboSirapN","text_ar":"تَبْصِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to understand the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rendered it apparent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plainly apparent, conspicuous, manifest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evident."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buS~irato bidimaAmK","text_ar":"بُصِّرَتْ بِدِمَامٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of the feathers of an arrow,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They were besmeared"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlbaSiyrapi","text_ar":"بِالبَصِيرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with blood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were strengthened and fastened with glue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A4-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bS~r","text_ar":"بصّر"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taboSiyrN","text_ar":"تَبْصِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AbSr","text_ar":"ابصر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"came,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the city of El-Basrah"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaSorap","text_ar":"البَصْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (S, M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","Msb","M"]},{"entry_id":"n2642","headword_ar":"بَصْرٌ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSorapN","text_ar":"بَصْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places: and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buSorapN","text_ar":"بُصْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2643","headword_ar":"بُصْرٌ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thickness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything; (M;) as of the heaven, (TA,) or of each heaven [of the seven heavens], (S, A, TA,) and of the earth, [or of each of the seven earths,] and of the skin of a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":211},{"kind":"text","text":"man, (TA,) and of a garment, or piece of cloth. (A.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawobN jay~idu AlbuSori","text_ar":"ثَوْبٌ جَيِّدُ البُصْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thick garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuborN","text_ar":"صُبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", formed by transposition, signifies the same. (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sbr","text_ar":"صبر"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A side:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: (S, K:) formed by transposition from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuborN","text_ar":"صُبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Cotton:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) whence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSiyrapN","text_ar":"بَصِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “an oblong piece of cotton cloth.” (TA.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSorapN","text_ar":"بَصْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["TA","S","A","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n2644","headword_ar":"بِصْرٌ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSorapN","text_ar":"بَصْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n2645","headword_ar":"بَصَرٌ","root":"bSr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sense of sight,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eye:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"light whereby the organ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sight"},{"kind":"text","text":"] ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AljaAriHap","text_ar":"الجَارِحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perceives the things seen"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuboSaraAt","text_ar":"المُبْصَرَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (Msb:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboSaArN","text_ar":"اَبْصَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, Msb, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaApu","text_ar":"صَلَاةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaSari","text_ar":"البَصَرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The prayer of sunset:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of daybreak:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because performed when the darkness becomes mixed with the light: (TA:) or because performed when the stars are seen: also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaApu Al$~aAhidi","text_ar":"صَلَاةُ الشَّاهِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$hd","text_ar":"شهد"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or because performed at a time when the eyes see corporeal forms, after the intervention of darkness, or before it. (JM.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiyahu baSarFA","text_ar":"لَقِيَهُ بَصَرًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He met him when eyes saw one another:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the beginning of darkness, when there remained enough light for objects to be distinguished thereby:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[accord. to some,] the noun is used [in the sense which it here bears] only as an adv. n. [of time]. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotuhu bayona","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُهُ بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samoEi AlA^aroDi wabaSarihaA","text_ar":"سَمْعِ الاَرْضِ وَبَصَرِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw him in a vacant tract of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the earth, where nothing but it heard or saw me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samoEN","text_ar":"سَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.] ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSiyrapN","text_ar":"بَصِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first sentence, in four places. ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eye;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baASirapN","text_ar":"بَاصِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayonN","text_ar":"عَيْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but of the masc. gender: (TA:) pl. as above: (Kur ii. 6, &c.:) but the sing. is also used in a pl. sense [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samoEN","text_ar":"سَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"smE","text_ar":"سمع"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See two exs. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baSiyrpN","text_ar":"بَصِيرةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Lth","S","M","K","Msb","TA"]}]}}